            #loading {
                direction: rtl
            }

            #loading:before {
                content: ' ';
                display: block;
                position: fixed;
                top: 0;
                right: 0;
                bottom: 0;
                left: 0;
                background-color: rgba(255,255,255,.3);
                z-index: 1000
            }

            #loading-view {
                background-color: #e7ebf0;
                position: absolute;
                left: 50%;
                top: 50%;
                margin-left: -80px;
                margin-top: -45px;
                padding: 15px;
                z-index: 10000000;
                -webkit-border-radius: 15px;
                -moz-border-radius: 15px;
                border-radius: 15px
            }

            #loading p {
                color: #000;
                display: inline-block;
                margin-right: 10px
            }

            .bounce-ball {
                position: relative;
                display: inline-block;
                height: 37px;
                width: 15px
            }

            .bounce-ball:before {
                position: absolute;
                content: '';
                display: block;
                top: 0;
                width: 15px;
                height: 15px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                background-color: #fbae17;
                -webkit-transform-origin: 50%;
                transform-origin: 50%;
                -webkit-animation: bounce .5s alternate infinite ease;
                animation: bounce .5s alternate infinite ease
            }

            @-webkit-keyframes bounce {
                0% {
                    top: 30px;
                    height: 5px;
                    border-radius: 60px 60px 20px 20px;
                    -webkit-transform: scaleX(2);
                    transform: scaleX(2)
                }

                35% {
                    height: 15px;
                    border-radius: 50%;
                    -webkit-transform: scaleX(1);
                    transform: scaleX(1)
                }

                100% {
                    top: 0
                }
            }

            @keyframes bounce {
                0% {
                    top: 30px;
                    height: 5px;
                    border-radius: 60px 60px 20px 20px;
                    -webkit-transform: scaleX(2);
                    transform: scaleX(2)
                }

                35% {
                    height: 15px;
                    border-radius: 50%;
                    -webkit-transform: scaleX(1);
                    transform: scaleX(1)
                }

                100% {
                    top: 0
                }
            }
        </style>

            window.onload = function() {
                document.getElementById("loading").remove()
            }
